articles.author: ABC News
articles.title: Matildas take down Denmark after superb Katrina Gorry goal and Caitlin Foord's double - ABC News
articles.description: Three second-half goals, including superb strikes by Katrina Gorry and Cailtin Foord, give the Matildas their first victory against a home side in Europe in almost a decade.
articles.content:
The Matildas have scored their best victory for a year, capping their European road trip with a 3-1 win against Denmark in Viborg. 
  • The Matildas conceded a goal in the opening minute
